title: Run Node_exporter With a Custom Metrics Directory
tags: @zettel _method prometheus node_exporter
roam-id: a4bae9c3-3b97-4817-8e0c-f14384102e86
type: text/markdown

run it with your systemd service like that

``` shell
/opt/grafana/node_exporter --collector.textfile.directory=/var/prometheus_metrics/
```
